oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Early Registration Encouraged for the 1981 Convention
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: N/A, N/A
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: REGISTRATION INFORMATIONWHOLE CONVENTION registration includes the 5 days of lectures, workshops and roundtables; also lunch on Friday and the Banquet dinner with entertainment Saturday evening.SATURDAY AND SUNDAY registration includes the workshops, lectures and round table on Saturday and Sunday, also the Banquet dinner and entertainment Saturday evening.VETERINARY SEMINAR is a separate program that begins Saturday noon and continues through Sunday.Convention registration does not include hotel accommodations or individual aviary and park rours that are also available.Â
